                            <votes>0</votes>
                                    <watches>1</watches>
                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="32871" author="pjones" created="Thu, 29 Mar 2012 18:30:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="28441" author="yong.fan" created="Sat, 11 Feb 2012 09:39:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;All the &quot;group_upcall&quot; in the manual should be replaced with &quot;identity_upcall&quot;, not only for the section &quot;33.1. User/Group Cache Upcall&quot;, but also for all the manual parts. The others to be updated include:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) &quot;mds_grp_downcall_data&quot; =&amp;gt; &quot;identity_downcall_data&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
2) &quot;l_getgroups&quot; =&amp;gt; &quot;l_getidentity&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
3) &quot;group_info&quot; =&amp;gt; &quot;identity_info&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
4) In lustre-1.8, &quot;group_upcall&quot;/&quot;group_info&quot; were under /proc/fs/lustre/mds/${mdsname}/&lt;br/&gt;
   But in lustre-2.x, &quot;identity_upcall&quot;/&quot;identity_info&quot; are under /proc/fs/lustre/mdt/${mdtname}/&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="28381" author="rhenwood" created="Fri, 10 Feb 2012 15:53:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Assuming the answer to the question above is &apos;yes&apos;, the following change is available for review:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,2130&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,2130&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="28380" author="rhenwood" created="Fri, 10 Feb 2012 15:46:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Do the changes to identity_upcall also mean &apos;group_info&apos; should be changed to &apos;identity_info&apos;?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-manual/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/lustre_manual.html#id2800039&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-manual/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/lustre_manual.html#id2800039&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
